data.description: ***Open House Saturday 22nd 11am-1p**** Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home only a short drive to the center of Crestview on a quiet road. The living room has a wonderful vaulted ceiling and natural stone fireplace with stunning mantle piece which adds character to the room.  The kitchen and dining room with ceramic tile offers ample cabinet space and gas oven/stove with direct access to the attached garage. The 2 guests bedrooms are bright with lots of natural light and share a bathroom. The spacious master suite with a vaulted ceiling and ensuite bathroom. Ample closet space with custom built shelving. This delightful home with new windows throughout in 2019, brand new water heater installed in May 2021, and has been freshly painted and is move in ready. Located in the sort after area for Anticoch school just a short 3minute drive, the house is also located on the school bus route. This home will not be on the market long and has been priced to sell.
